How do you run jascript ?
Javascript is being run in the browser. In a way to run Javascript we need a javascript engine(V8).

A javascript engine is a program that execue javascript code.

Can You run javaScript without the browser? 
With node js you can run javascript without the browser.
Node is a javascript runtime.

What is a Javascript Runtime ?
Runtime is a javascript eniroment. An environment that allows us to run javascript as well as do some extra.
Node has the V8 engine that makes our javascript code run efficiently.
If you want to read file or write file or maybe access database or write something, Thats where libuv comes in.
Node js is simply a way to give or javascript to the javascript environment.

Is a brower a javascript Runtime ?
Yes a web browser is a javascript Runtime because it has the javascript engine embedded in it.